dc:description: Buff clay with red glaze.  Nozzle end missing.  Plain rim divides at nozzle and two ends terminate in volutes.  Small stamped circle on either side.  Three circular grooves slope down from rim to discus.  Ram facing right in center.  Ring handle, two grooves on upper half.  Circular reverse set off by groove.
